  "prompt": "Where is a reliable mobile repair shop to get my phone screen replaced in Kolkata?",
  "response": "In Kolkata, there are several reliable mobile repair shops where you can get your phone screen replaced. Here are a few options you might consider:\n\n1. **Mobile Repair Centers**: Look for authorized service centers of your phone's brand (like Apple, Samsung, Xiaomi, etc.) as they typically offer reliable service with genuine parts.\n\n2. **Techy**: This is a popular repair chain in Kolkata that provides quick and reliable mobile repair services, including screen replacements.\n\n3. **The Mobile Doctor**: Known for efficient and quality service, this shop handles various mobile repairs, including screen replacements.\n\n4. **Kolkata Mobile Repair**: A local shop that specializes in mobile phone repairs and is known for reasonable prices and good service.\n\n5. **iFix**: iFix offers a range of repair services and is known for its customer service in Kolkata.\n\n6. **iRepair**: This service is well-rated for mobile repairs and offers quick service for screen replacements.\n\nBefore deciding, it\u2019s advisable to check online reviews, ask for warranty on repairs, and ensure they use quality parts. It's also a good idea to call ahead and inquire about the cost and time for the repair.",
